OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry
OL,6,Fovernight with clear spells, however
OL,7,Fsome higher cloud is likely to thicken
OL,8,Ffrom the west. The clear spells will
OL,9,Fallow for some mist or fog patches to
OL,10,Fdevelop by dawn. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FBrighter spells likely at
OL,13,Ffirst, and soon feeling warm in any
OL,14,Fsunshine. Cloud then thickens during
OL,15,Fthe afternoon, with outbreaks of rain
OL,16,Fpossible later. Breezy later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
