OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FChilly
OL,6,Fstart Friday then sunny intervals,
OL,7,Fcloud thickening later. Rain and
OL,8,Fstrong winds Saturday morning,
OL,9,Fisolated showers later. Sunshine and
OL,10,Fshowers Sunday. Temperatures near
OL,11,Faverage for April.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
